title: Sun Self Tanning Lotion Ultra Dark Instant Tint - Dark 8oz/236ml
description: Achieve a deep, natural-looking tan for the face and body while avoiding the harmful rays of the sun with Sun Laboratories Ultra Dark Lotion. This highly moisturizing formula coats the skin in an instant dose of color to prevent streaking or patchiness. Its non-clogging formula is ideal for all skin types, even sensitive.
